# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millss5.rpy:12
translate portuguese millss5_5ac69de4:

    # bs "Of course I do."
    bs "Claro que sim."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millss5.rpy:14
translate portuguese millss5_e07c76e1:

    # bs "I get to help resolve conflicts. I get to argue with people, which has always been fun for me."
    bs "Posso ajudar a resolver conflitos. Posso discutir com as pessoas, o que sempre foi divertido para mim."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millss5.rpy:15
translate portuguese millss5_24274416:

    # bs "Plus, they pay me so much I can pretty much do whatever I want to during my off time."
    bs "Além disso, pagam-me tanto que posso fazer praticamente o que quiser no meu tempo livre."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millss5.rpy:17
translate portuguese millss5_161e4ea7:

    # bs "So yeah, being a lawyer is great. There's not another profession I'd rather have."
    bs "Por isso, sim, ser advogada é ótimo. Não há outra profissão que preferisse ter."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millss5.rpy:18
translate portuguese millss5_93ebb2a5:

    # pc "Is there anything you don't like about it?"
    pc "Há alguma coisa de que não gostes nisso?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millss5.rpy:20
translate portuguese millss5_d60c47fa:

    # bs "Hm... I guess there's times when you get some asshole client that is hard to deal with."
    bs "Hum... Acho que há alturas em que se tem um cliente idiota com quem é difícil lidar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millss5.rpy:21
translate portuguese millss5_41f32e88:

    # bs "When you're a defense attorney, you still have to defend those people, even if you don't like them."
    bs "Quando se é advogado de defesa, ainda se tem de defender essas pessoas, mesmo que não se goste delas."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millss5.rpy:23
translate portuguese millss5_7e4bb0c8:

    # bs "But I don't do that anymore."
    bs "Mas já não faço isso."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millss5.rpy:25
translate portuguese millss5_9c43dff4:

    # bs "Now, if I don't like a client, I can just tell them to go find another lawyer to represent them."
    bs "Agora, se não gosto de um cliente, posso simplesmente dizer-lhe para procurar outro advogado para o representar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millss5.rpy:27
translate portuguese millss5_d1c854d2:

    # bs "Oh! All the politics is another thing that is frustrating."
    bs "Ah! Toda a política é outra coisa que é frustrante."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millss5.rpy:28
translate portuguese millss5_ddef5d36:

    # bs "Having to deal with judges, DAs, all those elected positions. Huge pain in the ass."
    bs "Ter de lidar com juízes, procuradores, todos esses cargos eleitos. Um enorme chato."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millss5.rpy:30
translate portuguese millss5_6a5cbc31:

    # bs "They're always torn between doing what's right and doing what looks good, so that they get elected again."
    bs "Estão sempre divididos entre fazer o que está certo e fazer o que fica bem, para que sejam reeleitos."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millss5.rpy:31
translate portuguese millss5_eaa6839d:

    # bs "It's all bullshit."
    bs "É tudo uma treta."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millss5.rpy:32
translate portuguese millss5_c6578e4e:

    # bs "I much prefer the civil courts. I've never been much good at politics."
    bs "Prefiro muito mais os tribunais civis. Nunca fui muito bom em política."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millss5.rpy:34
translate portuguese millss5_64091c16:

    # bs "I find it's less about being right and more about being likeable, and I just don't care if people like me."
    bs "Acho que tem menos a ver com estar certo e mais com ser simpático, e eu simplesmente não me importo se as pessoas gostam de mim."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millss5.rpy:38
translate portuguese millss5_234384fa:

    # bs "Ha! Don't get smart with me."
    bs "Ha! Não venhas com espertices."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millss5.rpy:41
translate portuguese millss5_b8412935:

    # bs "Do you?"
    bs "Gostas?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millss5.rpy:42
translate portuguese millss5_584dcad8:

    # bs "Wait until you get to know me better. See how you feel then."
    bs "Espera até me conheceres melhor. Vê como te sentes nessa altura."

